---
import { TextSection } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Page.astro';

const seo = {
  title: `Legal | JC Immigration`,
  description: `General legal information for JC Immigration.`,
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>
  <TextSection narrow>
    <h1>Legal Information</h1>

    <p>The information on this website is provided for general information only and does not create a consultant-client relationship.</p>

    <h2>Consultations</h2>

    <p>Advice about immigration options depends on the facts of each matter. JC Immigration reviews client circumstances before recommending next steps.</p>

    <p>Clients are responsible for providing complete and accurate information, documents, and updates that may affect an application.</p>

    <p>Immigration rules, processing times, and government requirements may change. We help clients understand current requirements when preparing a file.</p>

    <p>Submitting an application does not guarantee approval. Final decisions are made by the relevant government authority.</p>

    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

    <p>
      Information submitted through this website is used to respond to inquiries and coordinate consultations. Do not send sensitive documents until a secure intake process has been arranged.
    </p>

    <p>For questions about privacy or legal information, contact JC Immigration directly.</p>
  </TextSection>
</Layout>
